data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Iso2God allows you to convert an Xbox 360 ISO image to a Games on Demand container, without having to burn the image to optical media to rip it using NXE.
This application does not contain or utilise any source code produced, or derived from, any works contained in or associated with the Microsoft Xbox 360 SDK.
XexTool is used to perform decryption and decompression of XEXs. Huge thanks to xorloser for his work!
FTP support provided by the open source edtFTPnet library from Enterprise DT.
